column3: “Looks fire of course. Nice bright lime green buds covered in trichs. Has an awesome sweet taste to it that packs some serious flavor. A very nice relaxing stone. Something to kick back and watch a show to and slip slide away into mellow ZZzzzz's. Would def recommend”

“Anise! I'm not a fan so this was torture, but if you like the taste of black licorice you'll love this flower. Otherwise a very heavy sleepy Indica. Would be perfect for bedtime if I didn't feel the need to scrub my tongue of the taste...”

“This is the bed time special. Delicious taste, high is mellow AF, and you won’t need much. if you come across it and you need something for sleep it’s a sure go. pairs excellent with tobacco if that’s your thing. in a piece wanna slow roast for sure, so as to savor the taste”
“love this bud and the name is the same as my favorite go to music”

“Wow what can I say  about Jellyroll besides a must get indica in my book. Very very flavorful buds. If you  love purple, this Is a perfect  strain to just sit back and ride the waves . This is what I call  fine caviar.”
“Super chill. I want to put two p's in supper :)”
“This strand and some reggae music is so dangerous this is the ultimate chill”
